entries.name: Sentinel
entries.description: The Sentinel is itself a Governor and Pauser in the bridge contracts. It allows additional Sentinel-Governors to make changes in its name that can be restricted by Guards changing the Sentinel's relaxed state.

numRelaxedGuards.description: Number of relaxed guards in the Sentinel.

relaxThreshold.description: Threshold of relaxed Guards needed to relax the Sentinel

relaxed.description: An unrelaxed Sentinel allows only parameter changes in the Bridge that would make it more secure (decrease limits, increase delay period etc.)
